<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL34">
<l>uḷḷattē yuṟaiyu mālai yuḷḷuvā ṉuṇarvoṉ ṟillāk</l>
<l>kaḷḷattē ṉāṉun toṇṭāyt toṇṭukkē kōlam pūṇṭē</l>
<l>ṉuḷḷuvā ruḷḷiṟ ṟellā muṭaṉirun taṟiti yeṉṟu</l>
<l>veḷkippō yeṉṉuḷ ḷēnāṉ vilavaṟac cirittiṭ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, a deceitful person, who do not have any discernment to think about</l>
<l rend="indent">Māl who dwells in the heart,</l>
<l>became [Your] servant and put on the external appearance of [Your] devoted servant.</l>
<l>I became ashamed within myself thinking that</l>
<l>You will know all the thoughts of those who think</l>
<l rend="indent"> being with [them]</l>
<l>and laughed so that [my] ribs broke.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
